**********************************************************************
MAUI show image example code
**********************************************************************
What this example does:
    - 'show_img' displays an IFF image file for about 10 seconds. The 
      image filename must be included on the command line.

**********************************************************************
System requirements:
  - A working MAUI environment is assumed.
  - The demo requires that gfx is in memory.
  - The demo requires that mfm is in memory.
  - IFF assets must be available
 
*********************************************************************
Directories: 
  - Source code 
       $MWOS/SRC/MAUI/DEMOS 
        
*********************************************************************
To make this example:
  - From the source file directory type:
% os9make

*********************************************************************

